<p>We are a multidisciplinary collective of researchers accross borders that join forces to explore questions related with the dynamics of social systems.
Currently our members are located in Amsterdam (University of Amsterdam) and Lisbon (Universidade Nova de Lisboa), and we welcome further researchers interested in join our collective, in particular from different regions and/or countries.</p>

<p>Currently, the scope of our activities include:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The organization of seminars and discussion groups</li>
  <li>Supervision of MSc and PhD students</li>
  <li>Joint research streams</li>
  <li>Fundraising through the joint EU-level grant applications and/or support for local applications</li>
</ul>

<p>Our research spans a broad range of specific topics including, but not limited, to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Models of Opinions, Behaviours, and Innovations Spreading</li>
  <li>Emergence and evolution of Cooperation and Altruism in Multiagent Systems</li>
  <li>The role of Social Networks in Social Dynamics</li>
  <li>Application of Complex Systems to understand socio-economic dynamics</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

